He leído los 4 archivos clave del proyecto `encuesta/`:

- `cuestionario-pasteleria.php` — estructura HTML + tema Coffee-Varoch light
- `src/css/cuestionario.css` — 11KB de design system completo (variables, star rating, NPS, channel cards, etc.)
- `src/js/cuestionario-pasteleria.js` — 30KB con wizard de 5 pasos, auto-advance, validación y SweetAlert2
- `src/js/sample_cuestionario-pasteleria.js` — datos: 4 grupos de estrellas, 4 canales, NPS 1-10, 4 campos personales

Ahora conjuro la réplica completa como componente standalone vanilla (sin jQuery, sin backend) que respeta fielmente la paleta Coffee-Varoch light, el wizard de 5 pasos, toda la interactividad y el flujo de envío:

```html
<div class="w-full min-h-screen" style="font-family:'Inter',system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;">
<style>
/* ===== Coffee-Varoch Design System (light) — replica de cuestionario.css ===== */
.cv-root {
  --cv-primary:#003360; --cv-secondary:#F24444; --cv-info:#0078D7;
  --cv-success:#7AAB20; --cv-danger:#9E1B32; --cv-warning:#FFC107;
  --cv-disabled:#494C50; --cv-middle:#AAD3EB; --cv-aliceblue:#FAFCFF;
  --cv-default-bg:#F2F5F9; --cv-action:#2563EB; --cv-action-hover:#1D4ED8;
  --cv-accent:#60A5FA; --cv-soft:#FE9834;
  --cv-bg:#F2F5F9; --cv-card:#FFFFFF; --cv-border:#E2E8F0;
  --cv-text:#0F172A; --cv-muted:#64748B; --cv-label:#475569;
  --cv-input-bg:#F8FAFC; --cv-input-border:#CBD5E1;
  --cv-sidebar:#FFFFFF; --cv-header:#FFFFFF;
  --cv-hover:rgba(37,99,235,.08); --cv-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(15,23,42,.06);
}
.cv-root .cv-title{color:var(--cv-primary);font-weight:700;}
.cv-root .cv-text{color:var(--cv-text);}
.cv-root .cv-muted{color:var(--cv-muted);}
.cv-root .cv-label{color:var(--cv-label);font-size:11px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.03em;}
.cv-root .cv-page{background:var(--cv-bg);color:var(--cv-text);min-height:100vh;transition:background .2s ease,color .2s ease;}
.cv-root .cv-main-container{background:var(--cv-card);border-radius:10px;padding:20px;box-shadow:var(--cv-shadow);transition:background .2s ease;}
.cv-root .cv-card{background:var(--cv-card);border:1px solid var(--cv-border);border-radius:12px;box-shadow:var(--cv-shadow);transition:.2s ease;}
.cv-root .cv-input,.cv-root .cv-select,.cv-root .cv-textarea{width:100%;background:var(--cv-input-bg);border:1px solid var(--cv-input-border);border-radius:8px;padding:12px 14px;font-size:14px;color:var(--cv-text);transition:.15s;font-family:inherit;min-height:44px;box-sizing:border-box;}
.cv-root .cv-input:focus,.cv-root .cv-select:focus,.cv-root .cv-textarea:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--cv-action);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(37,99,235,.15);}
.cv-root .cv-input::placeholder{color:var(--cv-muted);opacity:.7;}
.cv-root .cv-textarea{resize:vertical;min-height:80px;}
.cv-root .cv-btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:6px;padding:10px 18px;border-radius:8px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid transparent;transition:.15s;text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;min-height:44px;}
.cv-root .cv-btn-primary{background:var(--cv-primary);color:#fff;}
.cv-root .cv-btn-primary:hover{background:#00264a;transform:translateY(-1px);}
.cv-root .cv-btn-action{background:var(--cv-action);color:#fff;}
.cv-root .cv-btn-action:hover{background:var(--cv-action-hover);transform:translateY(-1px);}
.cv-root .cv-btn-action:disabled{opacity:.5;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none;}
.cv-root .cv-btn-success{background:var(--cv-success);color:#fff;}
.cv-root .cv-btn-danger{background:var(--cv-danger);color:#fff;}
.cv-root .cv-btn-outline-action{background:transparent;color:var(--cv-action);border-color:var(--cv-action);}
.cv-root .cv-btn-outline-action:hover{background:var(--cv-action);color:#fff;}
.cv-root .cv-btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--cv-muted);}
.cv-root .cv-btn-ghost:hover{background:var(--cv-hover);color:var(--cv-action);}
.cv-root .cv-btn-sm{padding:8px 12px;font-size:13px;min-height:40px;}
.cv-root .cv-btn-lg{padding:14px 28px;font-size:16px;min-height:52px;}

/* Star rating */
.cv-root .cv-star-group{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.cv-root .cv-star{cursor:pointer;color:var(--cv-border);transition:.15s;padding:8px;}
.cv-root .cv-star:hover,.cv-root .cv-star.active{color:var(--cv-warning);}
.cv-root .cv-star.active-solid{color:#f59e0b;}
.cv-root .cv-star svg{width:48px;height:48px;}
.cv-root .cv-star:hover svg,.cv-root .cv-star.active svg{fill:currentColor;}

/* Check card */
.cv-root .cv-check-card{border:1.5px solid var(--cv-border);border-radius:12px;padding:22px 24px;cursor:pointer;transition:.15s;background:var(--cv-card);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:var(--cv-text);user-select:none;min-height:84px;}
.cv-root .cv-check-card:hover{border-color:var(--cv-action);background:var(--cv-hover);}
.cv-root .cv-check-card:active{transform:scale(.99);}
.cv-root .cv-check-card.active{border-color:var(--cv-action);background:rgba(37,99,235,.08);box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(37,99,235,.12);}
.cv-root .cv-check-card .cv-check-box{width:26px;height:26px;border:2px solid var(--cv-border);border-radius:7px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:.15s;flex-shrink:0;}
.cv-root .cv-check-card.active .cv-check-box{background:var(--cv-action);border-color:var(--cv-action);}
.cv-root .cv-check-card i,.cv-root .cv-check-card svg{width:22px;height:22px;color:var(--cv-muted);}
.cv-root .cv-check-card.active i,.cv-root .cv-check-card.active svg{color:var(--cv-action);}
.cv-root .cv-check-card .cv-check-box i,.cv-root .cv-check-card .cv-check-box svg{width:18px;height:18px;color:#fff;}

/* Rating row */
.cv-root .cv-rating-row{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:12px;padding:22px 16px;border:1px solid var(--cv-border);border-radius:10px;background:var(--cv-card);transition:.15s;text-align:center;}
.cv-root .cv-rating-row:hover{border-color:var(--cv-action);}
.cv-root .cv-rating-row.completed{border-color:rgba(122,171,32,.4);background:rgba(122,171,32,.04);}

/* NPS */
.cv-root .cv-nps-low{color:var(--cv-danger);}
.cv-root .cv-nps-mid{color:#b45309;}
.cv-root .cv-nps-high{color:var(--cv-success);}
.cv-root .cv-nps-card{border:1.5px solid var(--cv-border);border-radius:10px;padding:14px 6px;cursor:pointer;transition:.15s;background:var(--cv-card);text-align:center;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--cv-muted);user-select:none;min-height:48px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
.cv-root .cv-nps-card:hover{border-color:var(--cv-action);background:var(--cv-hover);}
.cv-root .cv-nps-card.active{border-color:var(--cv-action);background:rgba(37,99,235,.08);color:var(--cv-action);}
.cv-root .cv-nps-card.active-green{border-color:var(--cv-success);background:rgba(122,171,32,.08);color:var(--cv-success);}
.cv-root .cv-nps-card.active-yellow{border-color:var(--cv-warning);background:rgba(255,193,7,.08);color:#b45309;}
.cv-root .cv-nps-card.active-red{border-color:var(--cv-danger);background:rgba(158,27,50,.08);color:var(--cv-danger);}

/* Progress */
.cv-root .cv-progress{width:100%;height:6px;background:var(--cv-input-bg);border-radius:9999px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--cv-border);}
.cv-root .cv-progress-bar{height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--cv-action),var(--cv-info));border-radius:9999px;transition:width .3s ease;}

/* Section */
.cv-root .cv-section{border-top:1px solid var(--cv-border);padding-top:24px;margin-top:24px;}

/* Animations */
@keyframes cvFadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(6px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}
.cv-root .level-enter{animation:cvFadeIn .25s ease;}

/* Scrollbar */
.cv-root ::-webkit-scrollbar{width:6px;height:6px;}
.cv-root ::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:transparent;}
.cv-root ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--cv-border);border-radius:6px;}
.cv-root ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover{background:var(--cv-action);}

/* Step icon */
.cv-root .step-icon{width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;background:var(--cv-primary);flex-shrink:0;}

/* Success overlay */
.cv-root .cv-modal-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.5);z-index:100;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:1rem;overflow-y:auto;}
.cv-root .cv-modal{background:var(--cv-card);border-radius:16px;padding:32px 28px 28px;box-shadow:0 24px 60px rgba(15,23,42,.25);border:1px solid var(--cv-border);max-width:420px;width:100%;text-align:center;animation:cvFadeIn .3s ease;}
.cv-root .cv-modal-icon{width:88px;height:88px;margin:4px auto 12px;background:rgba(122,171,32,.15);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--cv-success);}
.cv-root .cv-modal-icon svg{width:48px;height:48px;}
.cv-root .cv-modal-title{color:var(--cv-primary);font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;}
.cv-root .cv-modal-body{font-size:14px;color:var(--cv-muted);line-height:1.6;}
.cv-root .cv-modal-body strong{color:var(--cv-text);}

/* Error msg */
.cv-root .cv-error-msg{color:var(--cv-danger);font-size:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-top:16px;}

/* Hidden */
.cv-root .cv-hidden{display:none !important;}

/* Responsive NPS grid */
.cv-nps-grid{display:grid;gap:4px;}
@media(min-width:640px){.cv-nps-grid{gap:8px;}}
</style>

<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
<script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<div class="cv-root">
<div class="cv-page cv-scroll min-h-screen overflow-y-auto" style="min-height:100vh;">
  <div class="cv-main-container" style="min-height:calc(100vh - 40px);padding:20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;max-width:900px;margin:20px auto;border-radius:12px;">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-4 level-enter">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-2">
        <h1 class="cv-title text-lg leading-tight">Cuestionario de Satisfaccion</h1>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-end gap-0.5 text-xs font-semibold leading-tight" style="color:var(--cv-muted);">
          <span id="cv-currentDate">-</span>
          <span id="cv-currentTime">-</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="cv-muted text-xs mt-0.5">Tu opinion nos ayuda a mejorar. Completa las secciones obligatorias y envia tu evaluacion.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Progress -->
    <div class="mb-6">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
        <span class="cv-label">
          <i data-lucide="activity" class="w-3 h-3 inline-block mr-1" style="vertical-align:middle;"></i> Progreso del cuestionario
        </span>
        <span id="cv-progressText" class="text-xs font-bold" style="color:var(--cv-action);">Paso 1 de 5</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cv-progress">
        <div id="cv-progressBar" class="cv-progress-bar" style="width:20%;"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Form -->
    <form id="cv-formCuestionario" novalidate class="flex-1">

      <!-- STEP 1: Stars -->
      <section class="cv-step level-enter" data-step="1" id="cv-step1">
        <div id="cv-step1_header"></div>
        <div id="cv-step1_body"></div>
        <div id="cv-step1_nav" class="flex items-center justify-between mt-5"></div>
      </section>

      <!-- STEP 2: Channel -->
      <section class="cv-step level-enter cv-hidden" data-step="2" id="cv-step2">
        <div id="cv-step2_header"></div>
        <div id="cv-step2_body"></div>
        <div id="cv-step2_nav" class="flex items-center justify-between mt-5"></div>
      </section>

      <!-- STEP 3: NPS -->
      <section class="cv-step level-enter cv-hidden" data-step="3" id="cv-step3">
        <div id="cv-step3_header"></div>
        <div id="cv-step3_body"></div>
        <div id="cv-step3_nav" class="flex items-center justify-between mt-5"></div>
      </section>

      <!-- STEP 4: Comments -->
      <section class="cv-step level-enter cv-hidden" data-step="4" id="cv-step4">
        <div id="cv-step4_header"></div>
        <div id="cv-step4_body"></div>
        <div id="cv-step4_nav" class="flex items-center justify-between mt-5"></div>
      </section>

      <!-- STEP 5: Data fields -->
      <section class="cv-step level-enter cv-hidden" data-step="5" id="cv-step5">
        <div id="cv-step5_header"></div>
        <div id="cv-step5_body"></div>
        <div id="cv-step5_nav" class="flex items-center justify-between mt-5"></div>
      </section>

      <!-- Error message -->
      <p id="cv-errorMsg" class="cv-error-msg cv-hidden">
        <i data-lucide="alert-triangle" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
        <span>Por favor completa todas las secciones obligatorias.</span>
      </p>
    </form>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="text-center py-4 cv-muted text-xs mt-auto" style="border-top:1px solid var(--cv-border);">
      <i data-lucide="coffee" class="w-3 h-3 inline-block mr-1" style="vertical-align:middle;"></i> Grupo Varoch - ERP-GV - CoffeeSoft
    </footer>

  </div>
</div>
</div>

<script>
(function(){
  'use strict';

  // ===== Sample data (from sample_cuestionario-pasteleria.js) =====
  const STEPS = [
    { id:1, title:'Calificacion de Servicio', desc:'Califica con estrellas cada area', icon:'star', component:'stars' },
    { id:2, title:'Como nos conociste?', desc:'Puedes seleccionar mas de una opcion', icon:'megaphone', component:'channel' },
    { id:3, title:'Nivel de Recomendacion', desc:'Del 1 al 10, que tanto recomendarias nuestra pasteleria?', icon:'trending-up', component:'nps' },
    { id:4, title:'Comentarios y Sugerencias', desc:'Opcional - Maximo 500 caracteres', icon:'message-square', component:'comment' },
    { id:5, title:'Datos para Promociones', desc:'Opcional - Recibe ofertas exclusivas en tu cumpleanos', icon:'gift', component:'fields' }
  ];

  const STAR_GROUPS = [
    { key:'rapidez',  label:'Rapidez'  },
    { key:'atencion', label:'Atencion' },
    { key:'variedad', label:'Variedad' },
    { key:'calidad',  label:'Calidad'  }
  ];
  const STAR_MAX = 5;

  const CHANNEL_OPTIONS = [
    { id:1, value:'Recomendacion',    label:'Recomendacion de un amigo o familiar', icon:'users',           is_other:false },
    { id:2, value:'Redes sociales',   label:'Redes sociales (Facebook, Instagram, etc.)', icon:'smartphone', is_other:false },
    { id:3, value:'Cliente frecuente',label:'Soy cliente frecuente',                  icon:'repeat',         is_other:false },
    { id:4, value:'Otro',             label:'Otro',                                    icon:'more-horizontal',is_other:true  }
  ];

  const NPS_MIN = 1, NPS_MAX = 10;
  const NPS_LABELS = { low:'Nada probable', high:'Muy probable', empty:'Selecciona una calificacion', detractor:'Poco probable', passive:'Probable', promoter:'Muy probable' };

  const COMMENT_MAX = 500;
  const COMMENT_PLACEHOLDER = 'Comparte tu experiencia, sugerencias o cualquier comentario que nos ayude a mejorar...';

  const DATA_FIELDS = [
    { name:'nombre',    type:'text',  label:'Nombre completo',     icon:'user',     placeholder:'Ej: Maria Garcia' },
    { name:'email',     type:'email', label:'Correo electronico',  icon:'at-sign',  placeholder:'Ej: maria@email.com' },
    { name:'telefono',  type:'tel',   label:'Telefono',            icon:'phone',    placeholder:'Ej: 961 123 4567' },
    { name:'cumpleanos',type:'date',  label:'Fecha de cumpleanos', icon:'calendar', placeholder:'' }
  ];

  // ===== State =====
  let currentStep = 1;
  const totalSteps = STEPS.length;
  let starsAdvanced = false, canalAdvanced = false, npsAdvanced = false;
  const starValues = {};
  const channelSelected = {};
  let npsValue = '';
  let commentValue = '';

  // ===== Helpers =====
  function qs(sel, ctx){ return (ctx || document).querySelector(sel); }
  function qsa(sel, ctx){ return Array.from((ctx || document).querySelectorAll(sel)); }
  function el(html){ const d = document.createElement('div'); d.innerHTML = html.trim(); return d.firstChild; }
  function lucideRefresh(){ if(window.lucide) lucide.createIcons(); }

  function stepOf(component){
    const idx = STEPS.findIndex(s => s.component === component);
    return {
      current: STEPS[idx] ? STEPS[idx].id : null,
      prev:    STEPS[idx-1] ? STEPS[idx-1].id : null,
      next:    STEPS[idx+1] ? STEPS[idx+1].id : null
    };
  }

  // ===== Clock =====
  function tickClock(){
    const now = new Date();
    qs('#cv-currentDate').textContent = now.toLocaleDateString('es-MX', { day:'2-digit', month:'2-digit', year:'numeric' });
    qs('#cv-currentTime').textContent = now.toLocaleTimeString('es-MX', { hour:'2-digit', minute:'2-digit', second:'2-digit', hour12:true });
  }

  // ===== Progress =====
  function updateProgress(){
    const pct = Math.round((currentStep / totalSteps) * 100);
    qs('#cv-progressBar').style.width = pct + '%';
    qs('#cv-progressText').textContent = 'Paso ' + currentStep + ' de ' + totalSteps;
  }

  // ===== Step header =====
  function renderStepHeader(stepId, title, desc, icon){
    const html = `
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-5">
        <div class="step-icon">
          <i data-lucide="${icon}" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="cv-title text-base">${title}</h2>
          <p class="cv-muted text-xs">${desc}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    `;
    qs('#cv-step' + stepId + '_header').innerHTML = html;
  }

  // ===== Step navigation =====
  function renderStepNav(stepId, prevStep, nextBtnHtml){
    const backHtml = prevStep !== null
      ? `<button type="button" class="cv-btn cv-btn-ghost cv-btn-sm" data-goto="${prevStep}"><i data-lucide="arrow-left" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Atras</button>`
      : '<div></div>';
    qs('#cv-step' + stepId + '_nav').innerHTML = backHtml + nextBtnHtml;
  }

  // ===== Star rating =====
  function renderStars(stepId){
    const groupHtml = STAR_GROUPS.map(group => {
      let stars = '';
      for(let i=1; i<=STAR_MAX; i++){
        stars += `<span class="cv-star" data-val="${i}" data-group="${group.key}"><i data-lucide="star"></i></span>`;
      }
      return `
        <div class="cv-rating-row mb-3" data-group="${group.key}">
          <span class="cv-label">${group.label}</span>
          <div class="cv-star-group">
            <input type="hidden" name="${group.key}" id="cv-val-${group.key}">
            ${stars}
          </div>
        </div>
      `;
    }).join('');
    qs('#cv-step' + stepId + '_body').innerHTML = groupHtml;

    // Bind star events
    qsa('#cv-step' + stepId + ' .cv-star').forEach(star => {
      star.addEventListener('click', function(){
        const value = parseInt(this.dataset.val, 10);
        const key = this.dataset.group;
        setStar(stepId, key, value);

        // Check if all groups completed
        const allDone = STAR_GROUPS.every(g => qs('#cv-val-' + g.key).value);
        if(allDone){
          autoAdvance('starsAdvanced', stepId);
        }
      });
    });

    // Hover preview
    STAR_GROUPS.forEach(group => {
      const row = qs('#cv-step' + stepId + ' .cv-rating-row[data-group="' + group.key + '"]');
      const stars = qsa('.cv-star', row);
      const hidden = qs('#cv-val-' + group.key);

      stars.forEach((star, i) => {
        star.addEventListener('mouseenter', function(){
          if(parseInt(hidden.value, 10) > 0) return;
          stars.forEach((s, n) => s.classList.toggle('active', n <= i));
        });
      });
      row.addEventListener('mouseleave', function(){
        if(parseInt(hidden.value, 10) > 0) return;
        stars.forEach(s => s.classList.remove('active'));
      });
    });

    lucideRefresh();
  }

  function setStar(stepId, key, value){
    const row = qs('#cv-step' + stepId + ' .cv-rating-row[data-group="' + key + '"]');
    const stars = qsa('.cv-star', row);
    const hidden = qs('#cv-val-' + key);
    hidden.value = value;
    starValues[key] = value;
    stars.forEach((s, i) => s.classList.toggle('active', i < value));
    row.classList.add('completed');
  }

  // ===== Channel selector =====
  function renderChannel(stepId){
    const cards = CHANNEL_OPTIONS.map(option => {
      const otherAttr = option.is_other ? ' data-is-other="1"' : '';
      return `
        <div class="cv-check-card" data-id="${option.id}" data-value="${option.value}"${otherAttr}>
          <div class="cv-check-box">
            <i data-lucide="check" class="text-white cv-hidden" style="width:18px;height:18px;"></i>
          </div>
          <i data-lucide="${option.icon}" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
          <input type="checkbox" name="canal[]" value="${option.value}" data-id="${option.id}" class="cv-hidden"${otherAttr}>
          <span>${option.label}</span>
        </div>
      `;
    }).join('');

    qs('#cv-step' + stepId + '_body').innerHTML = `
      <div id="cv-channelSelector">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-4">${cards}</div>
        <div id="cv-channelSelector_wrapOtro" class="cv-hidden">
          <label class="cv-label mb-1 block">
            <i data-lucide="pencil" class="w-3 h-3 inline-block mr-1" style="vertical-align:middle;"></i> Especifica otro canal
          </label>
          <input type="text" name="otro_canal" id="cv-channelSelector_inputOtro" class="cv-input" placeholder="Ejemplo: Vi su local pasando por la calle...">
        </div>
      </div>
    `;

    // Bind card clicks
    qsa('#cv-step' + stepId + ' .cv-check-card').forEach(card => {
      card.addEventListener('click', function(){
        toggleChannelCard(this);
        const values = getChannelValues();
        const nextBtn = qs('#cv-step' + stepId + '_nav .cv-btn-action');
        if(nextBtn) nextBtn.classList.toggle('cv-hidden', !values.otroActive);

        if(values.values.length > 0 && !values.onlyOther){
          autoAdvance('canalAdvanced', stepId);
        }
      });
    });

    // Bind "other" input
    const inputOtro = qs('#cv-channelSelector_inputOtro');
    if(inputOtro){
      inputOtro.addEventListener('input', function(){ this.style.borderColor = ''; });
      inputOtro.addEventListener('keydown', function(e){
        if(e.key === 'Enter' && this.value.trim()){
          e.preventDefault();
          autoAdvance('canalAdvanced', stepId, 0);
        }
      });
    }

    lucideRefresh();
  }

  function toggleChannelCard(card){
    const input = qs('input[type="checkbox"]', card);
    const isOther = card.getAttribute('data-is-other') === '1';
    const isChecked = !input.checked;
    input.checked = isChecked;
    card.classList.toggle('active', isChecked);
    const checkIcon = qs('.cv-check-box > i, .cv-check-box > svg', card);
    if(checkIcon) checkIcon.classList.toggle('cv-hidden', !isChecked);

    if(isOther){
      const wrap = qs('#cv-channelSelector_wrapOtro');
      const inputOtro = qs('#cv-channelSelector_inputOtro');
      if(isChecked){
        wrap.classList.remove('cv-hidden');
        inputOtro.setAttribute('required', 'required');
        setTimeout(() => inputOtro.focus(), 100);
      } else {
        wrap.classList.add('cv-hidden');
        inputOtro.removeAttribute('required');
        inputOtro.value = '';
        inputOtro.style.borderColor = '';
      }
    }
  }

  function getChannelValues(){
    const ids = [], values = [];
    const checked = qsa('#cv-channelSelector input[name="canal[]"]:checked');
    let otroActive = false, onlyOther = false;

    checked.forEach(c => {
      ids.push(c.dataset.id);
      values.push(c.value);
      if(c.getAttribute('data-is-other') === '1') otroActive = true;
    });

    const otroValor = qs('#cv-channelSelector_inputOtro') ? qs('#cv-channelSelector_inputOtro').value : '';
    if(checked.length === 1 && otroActive) onlyOther = true;

    return { ids, values, other: otroValor, otroActive, onlyOther };
  }

  // ===== NPS =====
  function renderNps(stepId){
    let cards = '';
    for(let n = NPS_MIN; n <= NPS_MAX; n++){
      cards += `<label class="cv-nps-card" data-val="${n}"><input type="radio" name="nps" value="${n}" class="cv-hidden" required><span>${n}</span></label>`;
    }

    qs('#cv-step' + stepId + '_body').innerHTML = `
      <div id="cv-npsRating">
        <div class="cv-card p-5 mb-2">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold cv-nps-low flex items-center gap-1">
              <i data-lucide="thumbs-down" class="w-3 h-3"></i> ${NPS_LABELS.low}
            </span>
            <span id="cv-npsRating_label" class="text-sm font-bold" style="color:var(--cv-muted);">${NPS_LABELS.empty}</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold cv-nps-high flex items-center gap-1">
              <i data-lucide="thumbs-up" class="w-3 h-3"></i> ${NPS_LABELS.high}
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="cv-nps-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(${NPS_MAX - NPS_MIN + 1}, minmax(0, 1fr));">
            ${cards}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    `;

    qsa('#cv-npsRating .cv-nps-card').forEach(card => {
      card.addEventListener('click', function(){
        const value = parseInt(this.dataset.val, 10);
        selectNps(this, value);
        npsValue = value;
        const nextBtn = qs('#cv-step' + stepId + '_nav .cv-btn-action');
        if(nextBtn){ nextBtn.disabled = false; }
        updateProgress();
        autoAdvance('npsAdvanced', stepId);
      });
    });

    lucideRefresh();
  }

  function selectNps(card, value){
    qsa('#cv-npsRating .cv-nps-card').forEach(c => c.classList.remove('active','active-green','active-yellow','active-red'));
    const radio = qs('input[type="radio"]', card);
    radio.checked = true;

    const promoterMin = 9, passiveMin = 7;
    let cls = 'active-red';
    if(value >= promoterMin) cls = 'active-green';
    else if(value >= passiveMin) cls = 'active-yellow';
    card.classList.add(cls);

    const lbl = qs('#cv-npsRating_label');
    if(value >= promoterMin){
      lbl.textContent = value + ' - ' + NPS_LABELS.promoter;
      lbl.style.color = 'var(--cv-success)';
    } else if(value >= passiveMin){
      lbl.textContent = value + ' - ' + NPS_LABELS.passive;
      lbl.style.color = '#b45309';
    } else {
      lbl.textContent = value + ' - ' + NPS_LABELS.detractor;
      lbl.style.color = 'var(--cv-danger)';
    }
  }

  // ===== Comment box =====
  function renderComment(stepId){
    qs('#cv-step' + stepId + '_body').innerHTML = `
      <div id="cv-commentBox">
        <div class="mb-2">
          <textarea name="comentarios" id="cv-commentBox_textarea" class="cv-textarea" maxlength="${COMMENT_MAX}" placeholder="${COMMENT_PLACEHOLDER}"></textarea>
          <div class="flex justify-end mt-1">
            <span id="cv-commentBox_counter" class="cv-muted text-xs">0 / ${COMMENT_MAX}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    `;

    const ta = qs('#cv-commentBox_textarea');
    ta.addEventListener('input', function(){
      qs('#cv-commentBox_counter').textContent = this.value.length + ' / ' + COMMENT_MAX;
      commentValue = this.value;
    });
  }

  // ===== Data fields =====
  function renderFields(stepId){
    const fieldsHtml = DATA_FIELDS.map(field => {
      return `
        <div>
          <label class="cv-label mb-1 block">
            <i data-lucide="${field.icon}" class="w-3 h-3 inline-block mr-1" style="vertical-align:middle;"></i> ${field.label}
          </label>
          <input type="${field.type}" name="${field.name}" id="cv-dataFields_${field.name}" class="cv-input" placeholder="${field.placeholder}">
        </div>
      `;
    }).join('');

    qs('#cv-step' + stepId + '_body').innerHTML = `
      <div id="cv-dataFields">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">${fieldsHtml}</div>
      </div>
    `;
    lucideRefresh();
  }

  // ===== Navigation =====
  function goStep(n){
    if(n < 1 || n > totalSteps) return;
    qsa('.cv-step').forEach(s => s.classList.toggle('cv-hidden', parseInt(s.dataset.step, 10) !== n));
    currentStep = n;
    updateProgress();
    window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
  }

  function autoAdvance(flagKey, fromStep, delay){
    if(window[flagKey] || currentStep !== fromStep) return;
    window[flagKey] = true;
    const s = stepOf(STEPS.find(st => st.id === fromStep).component);
    const ms = delay === undefined ? 650 : delay;
    if(ms > 0) setTimeout(() => goStep(s.next), ms);
    else goStep(s.next);
  }

  function nextFromOther(){
    const input = qs('#cv-channelSelector_inputOtro');
    if(!input.value.trim()){
      input.focus();
      input.style.borderColor = 'var(--cv-danger)';
      return;
    }
    const s = stepOf('channel');
    canalAdvanced = true;
    goStep(s.next);
  }

  // ===== Validation =====
  function validate(){
    for(const group of STAR_GROUPS){
      if(!qs('#cv-val-' + group.key).value){
        return { ok:false, step: stepOf('stars').current };
      }
    }
    if(!npsValue){
      return { ok:false, step: stepOf('nps').current };
    }
    const channel = getChannelValues();
    if(channel.otroActive && !channel.other.trim()){
      return { ok:false, step: stepOf('channel').current, focus:'#cv-channelSelector_inputOtro' };
    }
    return { ok:true };
  }

  // ===== Submit =====
  function handleSubmit(e){
    e.preventDefault();
    qs('#cv-errorMsg').classList.add('cv-hidden');

    const validation = validate();
    if(!validation.ok){
      qs('#cv-errorMsg').classList.remove('cv-hidden');
      goStep(validation.step);
      if(validation.focus) setTimeout(() => { const f = qs(validation.focus); if(f) f.focus(); }, 400);
      return;
    }

    // Simulate submission
    const folio = 'CV-' + Date.now().toString(36).toUpperCase().slice(-6);
    showSuccess(folio);
  }

  function showSuccess(folio){
    const overlay = el(`
      <div class="cv-modal-overlay" id="cv-successOverlay">
        <div class="cv-modal">
          <div class="cv-modal-icon">
            <i data-lucide="party-popper"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="cv-modal-title">Gracias por tu evaluacion!</div>
          <div class="cv-modal-body">
            <p>Folio: <strong>${folio}</strong><br>Tu opinion nos ayuda a seguir mejorando.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    `);
    document.querySelector('.cv-root').appendChild(overlay);
    lucideRefresh();

    setTimeout(() => {
      overlay.remove();
      resetAll();
    }, 2800);
  }

  // ===== Reset =====
  function resetAll(){
    // Stars
    qsa('.cv-rating-row').forEach(r => { r.classList.remove('completed'); qsa('.cv-star', r).forEach(s => s.classList.remove('active')); });
    STAR_GROUPS.forEach(g => { const h = qs('#cv-val-' + g.key); if(h) h.value = ''; });
    Object.keys(starValues).forEach(k => delete starValues[k]);

    // Channel
    qsa('.cv-check-card').forEach(c => { c.classList.remove('active'); const inp = qs('input[type="checkbox"]', c); if(inp) inp.checked = false; const ci = qs('.cv-check-box > i, .cv-check-box > svg', c); if(ci) ci.classList.add('cv-hidden'); });
    const wrap = qs('#cv-channelSelector_wrapOtro');
    if(wrap) wrap.classList.add('cv-hidden');
    const inputOtro = qs('#cv-channelSelector_inputOtro');
    if(inputOtro){ inputOtro.removeAttribute('required'); inputOtro.value = ''; inputOtro.style.borderColor = ''; }

    // NPS
    qsa('#cv-npsRating .cv-nps-card').forEach(c => c.classList.remove('active','active-green','active-yellow','active-red'));
    qsa('#cv-npsRating input[name="nps"]').forEach(r => r.checked = false);
    const npsLbl = qs('#cv-npsRating_label');
    if(npsLbl){ npsLbl.textContent = NPS_LABELS.empty; npsLbl.style.color = 'var(--cv-muted)'; }
    npsValue = '';
    const npsNext = qs('#cv-step3_nav .cv-btn-action');
    if(npsNext) npsNext.disabled = true;

    // Comment
    const ta = qs('#cv-commentBox_textarea');
    if(ta) ta.value = '';
    const counter = qs('#cv-commentBox_counter');
    if(counter) counter.textContent = '0 / ' + COMMENT_MAX;
    commentValue = '';

    // Data fields
    DATA_FIELDS.forEach(f => { const inp = qs('#cv-dataFields_' + f.name); if(inp) inp.value = ''; });

    // Error
    qs('#cv-errorMsg').classList.add('cv-hidden');

    // Flags
    starsAdvanced = false; canalAdvanced = false; npsAdvanced = false;

    // Go to first step
    goStep(1);
  }

  // ===== Init =====
  function init(){
    // Render all step headers
    STEPS.forEach(step => {
      renderStepHeader(step.id, step.title, step.desc, step.icon);
    });

    // Step 1: Stars
    renderStars(1);
    renderStepNav(1, null, '<button type="button" class="cv-btn cv-btn-action cv-btn-sm" data-goto="2">Siguiente <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i></button>');

    // Step 2: Channel
    renderChannel(2);
    renderStepNav(2, 1, '<button type="button" id="cv-step2_nav_next" class="cv-btn cv-btn-action cv-btn-sm cv-hidden">Siguiente <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i></button>');
    qs('#cv-step2_nav_next').addEventListener('click', nextFromOther);

    // Step 3: NPS
    renderNps(3);
    renderStepNav(3, 2, '<button type="button" class="cv-btn cv-btn-action cv-btn-sm" disabled data-goto="4">Continuar <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i></button>');

    // Step 4: Comments
    renderComment(4);
    renderStepNav(4, 3, '<button type="button" class="cv-btn cv-btn-action cv-btn-sm" data-goto="5">Continuar <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i></button>');

    // Step 5: Data fields
    renderFields(5);
    renderStepNav(5, 4, '<button type="submit" class="cv-btn cv-btn-primary cv-btn-lg"><i data-lucide="send" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Enviar evaluacion</button>');

    // Bind wizard navigation
    qs('#cv-formCuestionario').addEventListener('click', function(e){
      const btn = e.target.closest('[data-goto]');
      if(btn){ e.preventDefault(); goStep(parseInt(btn.dataset.goto, 10)); }
    });

    // Bind submit
    qs('#cv-formCuestionario').addEventListener('submit', handleSubmit);

    // Clock
    tickClock();
    setInterval(tickClock, 1000);

    // Initial progress
    updateProgress();

    // Lucide
    lucideRefresh();
  }

  if(document.readyState === 'loading'){
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', init);
  } else {
    init();
  }
})();
</script>
</div>
```

✨ He conjurado la réplica completa del cuestionario de satisfacción de pastelería en un componente standalone vanilla JS.

**Lo que replica fielmente del original:**

| Elemento | Origen | Réplica |
|---|---|---|
| Tema Coffee-Varoch light | `cuestionario.css` (40+ variables CSS) | Todas las variables inline en `.cv-root` |
| Wizard 5 pasos | `cuestionario-pasteleria.js` `sectionStep()` | 5 `<section>` con `data-step` |
| Estrellas (Rapidez, Atencion, Variedad, Calidad) | `starRatingComponent()` + `SAMPLE_CUESTIONARIO_STARS` | Render dinámico + hover preview + auto-advance |
| Selector de canales (4 opciones + "Otro") | `channelSelectorComponent()` + `SAMPLE_CUESTIONARIO_CHANNEL` | Cards checkbox + input condicional |
| NPS 1-10 (detractor/passive/promoter) | `npsComponent()` + `SAMPLE_CUESTIONARIO_NPS` | Grid 10 columnas + colores semánticos |
| Caja comentarios (500 chars) | `commentBoxComponent()` | Textarea + contador en vivo |
| Campos personales (nombre, email, teléfono, cumpleaños) | `dataFieldsComponent()` + `SAMPLE_CUESTIONARIO_DATA` | Grid 2 columnas |
| Auto-advance | `autoAdvance()` con flags `starsAdvanced`, `canalAdvanced`, `npsAdvanced` | Igual con `window[flagKey]` |
| Validación + error msg | `validate()` + `#errorMsg` | Validación de estrellas, NPS y "otro" canal |
| Success dialog | `showSuccess()` con SweetAlert2 | Modal custom Coffee-Varoch con `party-popper` |
| Reset completo | `resetAll()` | Limpia todos los componentes + vuelve al paso 1 |
| Reloj en vivo | `initClock()` / `tickClock()` | `setInterval` cada segundo |
| Barra de progreso | `renderProgress()` / `updateProgress()` | Gradiente action→info, % dinámico |
| Footer CoffeeSoft | `<footer>` con icono `coffee` | Igual |
